## Logging Strategy

| Location | Level | Message | Fields |
|----------|-------|---------|--------|
| Trace started | DEBUG | "Trace started" | `trace_id`, `object_id`, `region` |
| Span recorded | TRACE | "Span recorded" | `trace_id`, `span_id`, `kind`, `status` |
| Cross-region correlation | DEBUG | "Cross-region span correlated" | `trace_id`, `from_region`, `to_region`, `skew_ms` |
| Trace completed | INFO | "Trace completed" | `trace_id`, `e2e_latency_ms`, `symbols`, `success` |
| Clock skew detected | WARN | "Clock skew exceeds tolerance" | `trace_id`, `region`, `skew_ms`, `tolerance_ms` |
| Trace evicted | DEBUG | "Trace evicted" | `trace_id`, `age_ms`, `reason` |

